column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.devRad_u, p.devRadErr_u, p.expRad_u, p.expRadErr_u,  g.log_p5#_tot,  p.z, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.z > #
